    .headline
      font
        font What is it and how does it work?
    p.fontsize-base.u-marginbottom-60
      font
        font Grasruts is an online platform that aims to bring together CAMPAIGN CREATORS and SUPPORTERS, with the objective of COLLECTIVE COLLECTION OF FUNDS ("crowd funding"), to make feasible CAMPAIGNS.
        font Grasruts allows a CAMPAIGN CREATOR to present a CAMPAIGN idea and raise funds from SUPPORTERS interested in contributing to this CAMPAIGN.
        font CAMPAIGN CREATORS will also be able to offer the SUPPORTERS rewards, which will be defined by the CAMPAIGN CREATOR in each of these CAMPAIGNS.
        font Grasruts gathers the amounts disbursed by the SUPPORTERS destined to each of these CAMPAIGNS until the final deadline determined by the respective CAMPAIGN CREATORS.
      br/
      font
        font
          | When a CAMPAIGN ALL OR NOTHING reaches or exceeds the stipulated amount for its feasibility, within the term stipulated in the CAMPAIGN, the total amount raised of the SUPPORTERS will be available to be redeemed by the CREATOR OF THE CAMPAIGN, discounting the 5% + online payment charges.
        font In contrast, if a CAMPAIGN ALL OR NOTHING does not reach the requested amount, it will not be financed and Grasruts will provide the REIMBURSEMENT of the amounts paid.
        font For amounts paid by credit card, REFUND will be made on the next invoice or subsequent invoice of the credit card.
        font If the payment was made through a bank slip, the REFUND will be made through deposit into the bank account indicated by the SUPPORTER, as requested by Grasruts.
        font If the bank account is not provided for REFUND, Grasruts will keep the amounts available for REFUND for a maximum period of 90 days, as detailed in the item "Fees and Payments" below.
      br/
    .headline
