        font To be created, the FLEX CAMPAIGN does not need a closing date forecast.
        font The campaign may be open for up to 365 days from the date of publication of the CAMPAIGN.
      br/
      font
        font Unlike Grasruts ALL or NOTHING, the CAMPAIGN CREATOR receives everything he has been able to collect until the moment the FLEX CAMPAIGN is closed, provided that the amount collected exceeds the amount required by Grasruts as a minimum transfer.
      br/
      font
        font In Grasruts FLEX, in addition, the SUPPORTER may receive rewards, as long as this possibility is clear in the FLEX CAMPAIGN, but the SUPPORTER will not receive, in any event, the amounts destined for that CAMPAIGN, except in specific cases at Grasruts's discretion.
